## 7. Partition Table

Luôn dùng `partitions.csv` trong thư mục gốc:

```csv
# Name,   Type, SubType, Offset,  Size, Flags
app0,     app,  factory, 0x10000, 2M,
nvs,      data, nvs,     0x9000,  0x6000,
```

Ghi chú: `CONFIG_PARTITION_TABLE_OFFSET=0x8000` trong sdkconfig.
